@startuml UC-102_Activity
title UC-102: Launch New Program (Activity)

|Program Manager|
start
:Login to SCP;
if (Authenticated?) then (no)
  stop
endif

:Draft Program Definition (Title, Goals, Target);
:Configure Eligibility Rules (JSON DSL);
:Simulate Coverage against Population;

|Finance Manager|
:Review Cost Estimate;
if (Funds Available?) then (yes)
  :Allocate Budget Bucket;
  :Create Recurring Obligation Plan;
else (no)
  :Reject (Insufficient Funds);
  stop
endif

|Vertical Owner|
:Review Design & Policy Alignment;
if (Approved?) then (yes)
  :Digital Signature / Sign-off;
else (no)
  :Reject / Request Changes;
  stop
endif

|SCP Core: Programs|
:Change status to ACTIVE;
:Trigger enrollment windows;
:Notify regional Field Agents;

stop
@enduml
